dev.nokee.platform.jni

Interface JavaNativeInterfaceLibraryComponentDependencies

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentDependencies, JavaNativeInterfaceNativeComponentDependencies, JniLibraryDependencies, JniLibraryNativeDependencies

    public interface JavaNativeInterfaceLibraryComponentDependencies
extends JavaNativeInterfaceNativeComponentDependencies, ComponentDependencies, JniLibraryDependencies
    Allows the API, JVM implementation and native implementation dependencies of a Java Native Interface (JNI) library to be specified. It also allows JVM runtime only as well as native link only and runtime only dependencies of a JNI library to be specified.
    Since:
    0.5
